<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
        <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="/public/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
    
        <!-- JavaScript Libraries -->
        <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
        <script src="/public/scripts/webgazer.js"></script>
        <!-- <script src="/public/scripts/webgazerHandler.js"></script> -->
        <!-- Favicon -->
        <link rel="icon" href="/public/assets/favicon.webp" type="image/x-icon">
        <!-- Page Title -->
        <title>Security Control Simulation System</title>

    </head>

<body>
    <!-- Navigation Bar -->
    <nav class="custom-navbar">
        <div class="navbar-logo">
            <a>SCSS</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Scenarios Links Container -->
    <div class="info" id="description">
        <section class="info" id="no-advisor" style="display: none;">
            <h1><b>TASK DESCRIPTION</b></h1>
            <p>You are a cyber defence expert working within the Emergency Services cyberdefense devision, your role is to review incoming data packets and protect the network by classifying them as "Trusted", "Suspect", or "Hostile" based on the information provided. Misclassifications may lead to privacy or safety issues and impact the ability of the emergency services to function.</p>
            <button id="proceedToConfigWebGazer">Proceed</button>
        </section>
        <section class="info" id="ai-advisor" style="display: none;">
            <h1><b>TASK DESCRIPTION</b></h1>
            <p>You are a cyber defence expert working within the Emergency Services cyberdefense devision, your role is to review incoming data packets and protect the network by classifying them as "Trusted", "Suspect", or "Hostile" based on the information provided. Misclassifications may lead to privacy or safety issues and impact the ability of the emergency services to function.</p>
            <P>You have been provided with an A.I with access to the same information as yourself who will make recommendations which you can either select or ignore</P>
            <button id="proceedToConfigWebGazer">Proceed</button>
        </section>
        <section class="info" id="human-advisor" style="display: none;">
            <h1><b>TASK DESCRIPTION</b></h1>
            <p>You are a cyber defence expert working within the Emergency Services cyberdefense devision, your role is to review incoming data packets and protect the network by classifying them as "Trusted", "Suspect", or "Hostile" based on the information provided. Misclassifications may lead to privacy or safety issues and impact the ability of the emergency services to function.</p>
            <p>You have been provided with the selections of a previous participent who performed this task</p>
            <button id="proceedToConfigWebGazer">Proceed</button>
        </section>
    </div>

    <!-- modal for instructions for webgazer calibration -->
    <div id="modal" style="display: none; z-index: 1; width:100%; height:100%;">
        <section class="info text-center">
            <h1>WebGazer Eye Tracking Calibration</h1>
            <h2>Please allow webcam access before starting the calibration.</h2>
            <p>For optimum performance of the eye tracking software, please look directly at each green square whilst clicking 5 times, not looking away until it turns red.</p>
            <button type="button" id="continue">Continue</button>
        </section>
    </div>

</body>
<script>
    var condition = "<%= condition %>";

    switch (condition) {
        case "noAdvisor":
            document.getElementById("no-advisor").style.display = "block";
            break;
        case "aiAdvisor":
            document.getElementById("ai-advisor").style.display = "block";
            break;
        case "humanAdvisor":
            document.getElementById("human-advisor").style.display = "block";
            break;
    }

    document.getElementById("proceedToConfigWebGazer").addEventListener("click", () => {
        document.getElementById("description").style.display = "none";
        document.getElementById("modal").style.display = "block";
        document.getElementById("continue").addEventListener("click", () => {
            window.location.href = '/information/webgazerconfig';
        })
    })
</script>
</html>